		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">koitsu wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I dislike this kind of technology and can't stand seeing emulators running it; when animated it looks like an oil painting</div>
<br />Yet people admire oil paintings in museums, and the cel-shaded art style of <em>Skyward Sword</em> is based on paintings by Paul Cezanne, Camille Pissaro, and <a href="http://www.zeldauniverse.net/articles/skyward-swords-art-style-straddling-the-line-or-walking-a-new-path/" class="postlink">other Impressionists</a>.

		

